Extremely blessed to be launching this initiative in my community on March 2nd for Teen Mental Health Awareness day. This is a topic that has resonated with me since my journey from high school to college and now the NFL. I’ve always been led by the phrase “it takes a village” and believe it’s my duty to be that village for the youth. It has never been more pertinent than now to recognize the role mental health plays in our overall well-being. With that being said I’m excited to head back where it all began and talk with Tucker Highs’ Senior class!

Thank you @tuckerhighseniors for taking time out to be apart of our World Teen Mental Wellness Day. I hope you all enjoyed it, and that we were able to leave you with tools to better equip you for the challenges life tries to throws at you. YOU ALL MATTER especially to us! Continue to strive for greatness in all your future endeavors and embrace the transition! The village is always here when you need it so don’t be afraid to speak up! Thank you to the staff and volunteers who made this event so special. We are just getting started in our community & to our sponsors @supergoop , @inkandvolt , @prioritysports , @hexperformance , @azcardsinthecommunity , @littlewordsproject , @wearthepeace , @azcardinals , & @goodwipes , @universityofga we can’t thank you enough for helping us put together wellness bags for each student!

In light of the thanksgiving holidays our founder @jonledbetter13 has been busy! He had the opportunity of supporting the community this week through service! With all the amazing sponsors & volunteers he was able to donate $5000 to the @unitedfoodbank turkey drive. Serve hundreds of meals with @npfyphx & @phxmission which benefited some of the most amazing people/families. In all he was able to spread a bunch of love & cheer with his teammates from the @Arizonacardinals. Happy holidays from the Led A Better Way Family To Yours 🫶🏽

What a privilege it was to partner up with Celtic Property management & The Buffalo Troopers Motorcycle Club this year to spread the holiday cheers.Together we were able to donate about 2500 toys to two affordable housing complexes in the Phoenix area! The 290 families were overjoyed and so were we while passing out toys 🧸, pizza 🍕, and rocking out with the amazing @djtake2 🎵 . We are so thankful to our sponsors and the volunteers who made it all possible we are nothing without all of you!! 

Merry Christmas from Our family to yours! 🎄❤️🎄❤️🎄❤️
